quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"In the name of Allah, the Entirely Merciful, the Especially Merciful"
  1,2,"The gratitude/thanks/praise to God, the creation`s altogether`s/(universe`s) Lord"
  1,3,"The merciful, the merciful/most merciful"
  1,4,Owner/possessor (of) the Judgment Day/Resurrection Day
  1,5,"(Only) You we worship, and (only) You we seek help from"
  1,6,"Guide us (to) the way/road, the straight/direct"
  1,7,"(The) way/road (of) those You blessed on them, not (those) the angered on them, and nor the misguided"
